<section class="member-how-to">
    <h2>Daily planning</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>Top nav <strong>Planning</strong> → <a href="/planning/daily">/planning/daily</a>.</li>
        <li>Priorities: <a href="/planning/daily#today-work">/planning/daily#today-work</a>.</li>
        <li>Schedule: <a href="/planning/daily#daily-schedule">/planning/daily#daily-schedule</a>.</li>
    </ol>

    <h2>Start / end day</h2>
    <ol>
        <li><strong>Start Day</strong> and <strong>View Log</strong> on the daily plan page.</li>
        <li><strong>End Day</strong> when finished.</li>
    </ol>

    <h2>Todos</h2>
    <ol>
        <li><a href="/todo">/todo</a> or Planning → Todo List.</li>
    </ol>

    <h2>Try these links</h2>
